typeProperties.script:
source(output(
		ID as string,
		ID_VISITA as string,
		TIPO_VISITA as string,
		TIPO_VISITA_PTBR as string,
		TIPO_VISITA_ORDER as string,
		CLM_IND as string,
		RECORD_TYPE_ID as string,
		RECORD_TYPE_NAME as string,
		DATA as string,
		CICLO as string,
		TARGET_PER_ID as string,
		ROW_ID_TERRITORIO as string,
		SEMANA as string,
		FLAG_VISITA as string,
		TIPO_INTERACAO as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	wildcardPaths:['synapse/workspaces/gsk-synapse/warehouse/dash.email1to1/dim_interacao_visitas_realizadas.parquet'],
	partitionBy('hash', 1)) ~> dInteracaoVisitasRealizadas
source(output(
		ID as string,
		CICLO as string,
		ROW_ID_TERRITORIO as string,
		ROW_ID_CONTATO as string,
		VP as string,
		VR as string,
		VRE as string,
		VRT as string,
		PLANEJUN as string,
		REALUN as string,
		EFFECTIVE_CALLS as string,
		UNDER_CALLS as string,
		OVER_CALLS as string,
		OFF_TARGET_CALLS as string,
		TARGET_CUST as string,
		UNDER_TARGET as string,
		ON_TARGET as string,
		OVER_TARGET as string,
		EMAIL_CONSENT_KPI as string,
		AT_DESIRED_FREQUENCY as string,
		OVER_DESIRED_FREQUENCY as string,
		TIPO_INTERACAO as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	wildcardPaths:['synapse/workspaces/gsk-synapse/warehouse/dash.email1to1/dim_interacao_visitas_medicos.parquet'],
	partitionBy('hash', 1)) ~> dInteracaoVisitasMedicos
source(output(
		ID as string,
		CICLO as string,
		ID_ENVIO_EMAIL as string,
		ID_ATIV_EMAIL as string,
		TIPO_ATIV_EMAIL as string,
		DATA_ATIV_EMAIL as string,
		PRODUTO as string,
		ROW_ID_CONTATO as string,
		ROW_ID_TERRITORIO as string,
		DOCUMENTO_EMAIL as string,
		DESC_DOCUMENTO_EMAIL as string,
		ASSUNTO_EMAIL as string,
		TIPO_INTERACAO as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	wildcardPaths:['synapse/workspaces/gsk-synapse/warehouse/dash.email1to1/dim_interacao_email.parquet'],
	partitionBy('hash', 1)) ~> dInteracaoEmail
source(output(
		ID as string,
		ROW_ID_CONTATO as string,
		ROW_ID_TERRITORIO as string,
		CICLO as string,
		PRODUTO_FRANCHISE as string,
		FRANCHISE as string,
		SUB_CAT_FRANCHISE as string,
		PESO_FRANCHISE as string,
		TIPO_INTERACAO as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	format: 'parquet',
	wildcardPaths:['synapse/workspaces/gsk-synapse/warehouse/dash.email1to1/dim_interacao_visitas_franchise.parquet']) ~> dInteracaoVisitasFranchise
source(output(
		CRM_CICLO as string,
		MES as string,
		CICLO as string,
		CRM as string,
		MEDICO as string,
		TIPO as string,
		TIPOCONTATO as string,
		GRUPOPROMOCIONAL as string,
		ESPECIALIDADE as string,
		LOGRADOURO as string,
		COMPLEMENTO as string,
		BAIRRO as string,
		CIDADE as string,
		UF as string,
		CEP as string,
		BRICK as string,
		TELEFONEMEDICO as string,
		CELULARMEDICO as string,
		EMAIL_1_1 as string,
		ROW_ID_FUNCIONARIO as string,
		ROW_ID_TERRITORIO as string,
		ROW_ID_CONTATO as string,
		STATUS as string,
		QTD_VISITA_PLANEJADA_PAINEL as string,
		QTD_VISITA_REALIZADA_PAINEL as string,
		ESPECIALIDADE_02 as string,
		ESPECIALIDADE_03 as string,
		VP_PROX as string,
		STATUS_MEDICO as string,
		EMAIL_1_1_CONSENT as string,
		NETWORK_ID as string,
		RX_GIGYA_ID as string,
		VEEVA_ID as string,
		ROW_ID_CONTATO_EXT as string,
		EMAIL_MASS as string,
		EMAIL_MASS_CONSENT as string,
		CYCLE_PLAN as string,
		MERCADO as string,
		PRODUTO_PAINEL as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	ignoreNoFilesFound: false,
	limit: 100,
	format: 'parquet',
	wildcardPaths:['synapse/workspaces/gsk-synapse/warehouse/dash.email1to1/dim_painel_medico.parquet']) ~> ChavePainelInteracaoQuadrante
dInteracaoVisitasRealizadas, dInteracaoVisitasMedicos union(byName: true,
	partitionBy('hash', 1))~> VisRealizadastoVisMedicos
VisRealizadastoVisMedicos, dInteracaoEmail union(byName: true,
	partitionBy('hash', 1))~> Uniao1toEmail
Uniao1toEmail, dInteracaoVisitasFranchise union(byName: true,
	partitionBy('hash', 1))~> Uniao2toVisFranchise
RemoveColumns1 aggregate(groupBy(ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
		ROW_ID_CONTATO,
		CICLO),
	KEY_TERR_CONT_CICLO = sum(add(KEY_TERR_CONT_CICLO,1)),
	partitionBy('hash', 1)) ~> Aggregate1
Uniao2toVisFranchise keyGenerate(output(KEY_TERR_CONT_CICLO as long),
	startAt: 1L,
	partitionBy('hash', 1)) ~> SurrogateKey1
SurrogateKey1 select(mapColumn(
		ID_VISITA,
		TIPO_VISITA,
		TIPO_VISITA_PTBR,
		TIPO_VISITA_ORDER,
		CLM_IND,
		RECORD_TYPE_ID,
		RECORD_TYPE_NAME,
		DATA,
		CICLO,
		TARGET_PER_ID,
		ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
		SEMANA,
		FLAG_VISITA,
		TIPO_INTERACAO,
		ROW_ID_CONTATO,
		VP,
		VR,
		VRE,
		VRT,
		PLANEJUN,
		REALUN,
		EFFECTIVE_CALLS,
		UNDER_CALLS,
		OVER_CALLS,
		OFF_TARGET_CALLS,
		TARGET_CUST,
		UNDER_TARGET,
		ON_TARGET,
		OVER_TARGET,
		EMAIL_CONSENT_KPI,
		AT_DESIRED_FREQUENCY,
		OVER_DESIRED_FREQUENCY,
		ID_ENVIO_EMAIL,
		ID_ATIV_EMAIL,
		TIPO_ATIV_EMAIL,
		DATA_ATIV_EMAIL,
		PRODUTO,
		DOCUMENTO_EMAIL,
		DESC_DOCUMENTO_EMAIL,
		ASSUNTO_EMAIL,
		PRODUTO_FRANCHISE,
		FRANCHISE,
		SUB_CAT_FRANCHISE,
		PESO_FRANCHISE,
		KEY_TERR_CONT_CICLO
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> RemoveColumns1
Uniao2toVisFranchise select(mapColumn(
		ID_VISITA,
		TIPO_VISITA,
		TIPO_VISITA_PTBR,
		TIPO_VISITA_ORDER,
		CLM_IND,
		RECORD_TYPE_ID,
		RECORD_TYPE_NAME,
		DATA,
		CICLO,
		TARGET_PER_ID,
		ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
		SEMANA,
		FLAG_VISITA,
		TIPO_INTERACAO,
		ROW_ID_CONTATO,
		VP,
		VR,
		VRE,
		VRT,
		PLANEJUN,
		REALUN,
		EFFECTIVE_CALLS,
		UNDER_CALLS,
		OVER_CALLS,
		OFF_TARGET_CALLS,
		TARGET_CUST,
		UNDER_TARGET,
		ON_TARGET,
		OVER_TARGET,
		EMAIL_CONSENT_KPI,
		AT_DESIRED_FREQUENCY,
		OVER_DESIRED_FREQUENCY,
		ID_ENVIO_EMAIL,
		ID_ATIV_EMAIL,
		TIPO_ATIV_EMAIL,
		DATA_ATIV_EMAIL,
		PRODUTO,
		DOCUMENTO_EMAIL,
		DESC_DOCUMENTO_EMAIL,
		ASSUNTO_EMAIL,
		PRODUTO_FRANCHISE,
		FRANCHISE,
		SUB_CAT_FRANCHISE,
		PESO_FRANCHISE
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Select1
Select1, Aggregate1 lookup(Select1@ROW_ID_TERRITORIO == Aggregate1@ROW_ID_TERRITORIO
	&& Select1@ROW_ID_CONTATO == Aggregate1@ROW_ID_CONTATO
	&& Select1@CICLO == Aggregate1@CICLO,
	multiple: true,
	partitionBy('hash', 1),
	broadcast: 'auto')~> Lookup1
ChavePainelInteracaoQuadrante keyGenerate(output(KEY_TERR_CONT_CICLO as long),
	startAt: 1L) ~> KEYQUDINTPAINEL
KEYQUDINTPAINEL aggregate(groupBy(ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
		ROW_ID_CONTATO,
		CICLO),
	KEY_TERR_CONT_CICLO_TEMP = sum(add(KEY_TERR_CONT_CICLO,0)),
	partitionBy('hash', 1)) ~> KEYTERRCONTCICLO
KEYTERRCONTCICLO select(mapColumn(
		ROW_ID_TERRITORIO,
		ROW_ID_CONTATO,
		CICLO,
		KEY_TERR_CONT_CICLO_TEMP
	),
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> Select2
Lookup1 sink(input(
		{202012;REP 631711;CG804878;CLAUDIANE;CLAUDIANE BEATRIZ GURGEL DO AMARAL CANTO SALES;PORTO VELHO;RO;I+P;;20201127;AC0000977;CIRO FALCÃO MACEDO JÚNIOR;CIRO MACEDO JÚNIOR;CIRO;FALCÃO;MACEDO JÚNIOR;RIO BRANCO;AC;"AVENIDA GETÚLIO VARGAS} as string,
		{ 811  ";CARDIOLOGIA;;;;;NULL;NULL;;5569999256460;2020-12-03} as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> sink1
